Package com.tangosol.util.function

Interface Remote.LongToDoubleFunction

All Superinterfaces:
LongToDoubleFunction, Serializable
Enclosing class:
Remote
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public static interface Remote.LongToDoubleFunction extends LongToDoubleFunction, Serializable
Represents a function that accepts a long-valued argument and produces a double-valued result. This is the long-to-double primitive specialization for Remote.Function.

This is a functional interface whose functional method is LongToDoubleFunction.applyAsDouble(long).
